## Findings

### RCR-001

- Severity: P0
- Title: task detail progress/error contract is not implemented to AC-002
- Evidence:
  - `docs/product/acceptance-criteria.md`: `AC-002` 要求可查询任务状态、总数、已处理数、进度和错误信息。
